---
title: One-Pan Cheddar Chicken & Crispy Grains with Scallion Salsa & Sour Cream
description: For this one pan 15-minute meal, you’ll crisp up a grain blend that stars rice, bulgur, and barley, then finish with fully cooked chicken and a bright squeeze of lime juice. You’ll serve this wholesome bowl with a bevy of tasty toppings: melty white cheddar, scallion salsa, a drizzle of sour cream, and a dash of hot sauce.
